<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-allergic-to">(be) allergic to</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>对……过敏</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was allergic to cat fur and started sneezing when she brought her pet into the room.
他对猫的毛过敏，她把小猫带进屋后他就开始打喷嚏。</p><footer>人教⑩ – 2</footer></div></div>